363
00:24:06,730 --> 00:24:10,940
Inside people's hearts, there is
a deep, dark, frightening hole.

364
00:24:11,530 --> 00:24:14,280
This eventually becomes
a new tunnel.

365
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:20,620
